<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Registration Confirmation</h1>

<p>Dear {$name} {$surname},</p>

<p>thank you for your registration. Here are your registration details:</p>

<h2>Personal Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Username: {$username}</li>
    <li>Email: {$email}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Permanent Address</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Street: {$street}</li>
    <li>City: {$city}</li>
    <li>Postal Code: {$postal_code}</li>
    <li>Region: {$kraj}</li>
    <li>District: {$okres}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Correspondence Address</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Street: {$correspondence_street}</li>
    <li>City: {$correspondence_city}</li>
    <li>Postal Code: {$correspondence_postal_code}</li>
    <li>Region: {$correspondence_kraj}</li>
    <li>District: {$correspondence_okres}</li>
</ul>

<p>Best regards,<br>ECL</p>
</body>
</html>